### change_toolbar_thread_resolve_status
Mark a toolbar thread as resolved or unresolved.

| Field | Type | Required | Default | Description |
|-------|------|----------|---------|-------------|
| threadId | string | Yes | - | Thread ID to update |
| teamId | string | Yes | - | Team ID or slug |
| resolved | boolean | Yes | - | true to resolve, false to unresolve |

Example:
CallMcpTool({ server: "vercel", toolName: "change_toolbar_thread_resolve_status", arguments: { threadId: "thread_123", teamId: "team_abc", resolved: true } })

### get_toolbar_thread
Get a specific toolbar thread by ID.

| Field | Type | Required | Default | Description |
|-------|------|----------|---------|-------------|
| threadId | string | Yes | - | Thread ID to retrieve |
| teamId | string | Yes | - | Team ID or slug |

Example:
CallMcpTool({ server: "vercel", toolName: "get_toolbar_thread", arguments: { threadId: "thread_123", teamId: "team_abc" } })

### list_toolbar_threads
List Vercel toolbar comment threads for a team.

| Field | Type | Required | Default | Description |
|-------|------|----------|---------|-------------|
| teamId | string | Yes | - | Team ID or slug |
| projectId | string | No | - | Filter by project ID |
| branch | string | No | - | Filter by branch name |
| status | string | No | - | resolved or unresolved |
| page | string | No | - | Page path or glob |
| search | string | No | - | Search text in comments |
| limit | number | No | - | Maximum results (default 20) |
| offset | number | No | - | Pagination offset |

Example:
CallMcpTool({ server: "vercel", toolName: "list_toolbar_threads", arguments: { teamId: "team_abc", projectId: "prj_123", status: "unresolved" } })

